Distribution.
Amietophrynus s. chevalieri
(formerly usually referred to as
A. superciliaris
) is known from forests in Upper Guinea . At present the taxon is known from Liberia (
Hillers & Rödel 2007
), Sierra Leone (this paper;
Figs. 1
; 9g ); Guinea (
